meta {
  name: 03 - Get artist (warm)
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/catalog/artists/{{beatlesArtistMbid}}
}

headers {
  Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{sessionCookie}}
}

docs {
  Once the fetch-artist job completes, re-running this returns 200 with the
  artist row (MB id, name, sort name, country, founded/dissolved years,
  lastFetchedAt).
}
